The '''Underworld Inn''' was a small, run-down hotel located in the lower levels of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It had its own [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] as well as a small amount of rooms. [[Ferus Olin]], [[Trever Flume]], and members of the [[Erased]] stayed at this inn for a short time while searching for [[Fy-Tor-Ana|Solace]]. It was mentioned that it cost extra for towels and water.

